com.hcl.domino.design

Interface Column

  • All Superinterfaces:
    DesignElement

    public interface Column
extends DesignElement
    Access to a View or Folder column and its settings. This only focuses on settings that affect data access, not settings that affect display in Notes or Nomad Clients.
    Author:
    t.b.d
